{"tid":2450755,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港學術自由指數榮獲D級 教育局回應學術自由受基本法保障","createTime":"2021-03-17T15:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T17:00:03.000Z","uid":125168,"like":35,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"16e939a0310ed2014c368b77ca28054bfb709844","tid":2450755,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"香港學術自由指數跌至D級 排名在柬埔寨之後<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-rank-03172021055045.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-rank-03172021055045.html&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTwZ9jGrNtOn8RK6k%2FrDhOJo%3D&h=348e418c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-rank-03172021055045.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/htm/hk-rank-03172021055045.html/@@images/b09c62d7-b5f3-46ee-ae51-8b13a5940652.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fhtm%2Fhk-rank-03172021055045.html%2F%40%40images%2Fb09c62d7-b5f3-46ee-ae51-8b13a5940652.png&h=04cf6b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球公共政策研究所（Global Public Policy Institute）上周公布「全球學術自由指數」（Academic Freedom Index，AFi） 及評級，香港評分下跌，獲評Ｄ級，香港排名更在柬埔寨之後。報告作者認為，香港去年實施《國安法》，令高等學府面臨壓力大增。（方德豪  報道） <br />\n<br />\nAFi分數介乎於0至1，0為最差，1為最好；評分按一組5個指標計算，包括「研究及教學自由」、「學術交流及宣傳自由」、「院校自主」、「校園誠信」、「學術及文化表達自由」。報告又按各國的評分，把各國納入五個評級，A級最好，E級最差（見表）。報告指出，香港去年AFi為0.348分，較柬埔寨（0.381）、俄羅斯（0.374）等國家還要差。報告指出，香港的學術自由指數在過去5年內減少約0.15分。 <br />\n<br />\n關注全球高等院校新聞的University World News也在上周六（13日）引述全球學術自由指數作者的評論，指香港是其中一個於2019至2020年學術自由大幅倒退的地區，該媒體認為香港高教界多年來受壓，中共去年強推「港區國安法」亦令高等學府面臨壓力大幅增加，不少學者十分關注國安法會損蝕學術研究、交流及國際合作，而因應國安法的壓力，高教界取消多個校園活動，並點名提到香港中文大學與學生會「割席」一事。 <br />\n<br />\n香港教育局在回覆傳媒查詢時重申：香港學術自由受基本法保障。"},{"pid":"f7853c385a985edac27d480bc3cfa02cd7d730d6","tid":2450755,"uid":393145,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"1900-1945年有幾多年？<br />\n<br />\n8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣嘅城市講學術自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ba7e0d911a92fbfb00422533c214bb962a765f","tid":2450755,"uid":141668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"學術自由又腐乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ee99cbe6ac8468d83d9b6ea75c35141d6ba6af","tid":2450755,"uid":294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:33:51.000Z","msg":"＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊"},{"pid":"698ee335869fd60f4db0669507d3bc0a99edc42c","tid":2450755,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a4ba7e0d911a92fbfb00422533c214bb962a765f","tid":2450755,"uid":141668,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"學術自由又腐乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca1f8edb38c71025ec425ef19e381f5d52657ce","tid":2450755,"uid":103230,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:34:09.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n但基本法冇受任何保障呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6addecfde51c41bfcb9d49ede6ca5b57462a795","tid":2450755,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"咁國安法呢"},{"pid":"ade5e3d2f31a5ac0dc7f52d49ea02691026dd360","tid":2450755,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b44d9770119bb67b27cd2ab01a54d3cc8930412","tid":2450755,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"不過人大同國安高於基本法"},{"pid":"291c3c7776